N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1276.11 - Compliance

State Regulations

Except as hereinafter specifically provided, no tank
vehicle shall be used at the air terminal unless it complies fully with all the
provisions of the rules and regulations set forth in this Part and has been
inspected and registered in accordance herewith. Notes
